{"tid":289563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"若邦交全斷 前白宮官員葉望輝：該宣佈成為「台灣共和國」","createTime":"2017-06-19T06:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T10:38:16.000Z","uid":35790,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e2847c8395cbb5fd85f0c48bcff17d74d28d6e84","tid":289563,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T06:17:11.000Z","msg":"若邦交全斷 葉望輝：該宣佈成為「台灣共和國」　<br />\n<br />\n2017-06-18 14:33<br />\n<br />\n點閱：8520<br />\n<br />\n【壹電視報導】巴拿馬與台灣斷交後，今天北美洲台灣商會會議上，台商們同仇敵愾！駐美代表高碩泰更直言，這是中共這隻黑手明目張膽的操作。<br />\n<br />\n壹電視主播陳雅琳獨家專訪推動川蔡熱線的<span style=\"color: red;\">前白宮官員葉望輝，他更強調，如果中國要把台灣的外交關係都切斷的話，台灣是可宣佈成為「台灣共和國」的，他說台灣人民本來就有這個選擇權的</span>，而如果中國不想要這樣，那就請不要再攻擊台灣了，邏輯就這麼簡單。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nexttv.com.tw/news/realtime/international/11899348/若邦交全斷　葉望輝：該宣佈成為「台灣共和國」\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nexttv.com.tw%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F11899348%2F%E8%8B%A5%E9%82%A6%E4%BA%A4%E5%85%A8%E6%96%B7%E3%80%80%E8%91%89%E6%9C%9B%E8%BC%9D%EF%BC%9A%E8%A9%B2%E5%AE%A3%E4%BD%88%E6%88%90%E7%82%BA%E3%80%8C%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E5%85%B1%E5%92%8C%E5%9C%8B%E3%80%8D&d=iZ1a9SmCMlNlwUAqsoevFBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=90dc64ba\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nexttv.com.tw/news/realtime/international/11899348/若邦交全斷　葉望輝：該宣佈成為「台灣共和國」</a>　"},{"pid":"29f6a40fccaa6b1195c41b9ff36b03febe353892","tid":289563,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T06:18:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acd8b0889fdaeb8cb0a5d4476a6a9bd6b0b8cc8a","tid":289563,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T06:38:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0304cd7ce4157a761784f67e5977c54f8d10da6","tid":289563,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T09:40:26.000Z","msg":"自古以來台灣係中國不可分割一部份<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\